{"tid":1217872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[廣傳] 614！綠線遊車河功略！","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T16:32:34.000Z","uid":259319,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fcb61ee429821435edd677bc8156a571f5767b1c","tid":1217872,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"我發夢見到tg group有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日6月14號</span></span></span></span><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">綠線遊車河攻略</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上7:25前到達調景嶺站附近任何地方<br />\n早上7:30分全世界進入月台6-1車廂候車<br />\n早上7:35後第一班列車上車(如列車7:34開始停到7:35,等佢開左先計下一班)<br />\n到油麻地，車廂會極小人，不宜久留。於油麻地站離開，用各自方法前往黃埔<br />\n早上8:50 於黃埔5-1車卡重覆以上行為返回調景嶺站<br />\n到調景嶺，車廂會極小人，不宜久留。落車離開，用各自方法兜個圈，再集合<br />\n早上10:15 於調景嶺6-1車廂集合，重覆以上行為，到油麻地離開。<br />\n遊車河結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結：調景巔出發，來回1.5次，如果不幸脫隊，或者錯過集合時間，請於以上其中一個時間點重新加入<br />\n<br />\n個夢真係好真實，大家千祈唔好做呀，特別游車河嗰陣<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好跌親</span></span></strong></span></span>，阻住人返工返學就唔好啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好咁多人</span></strong></span></span>一齊遊呀，太多人會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">癱瘓交通</span></span></span>㗎，記住奉公守法呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"f67ddf49f98d5bb40e551a8f1ad1baee07dbeef3","tid":1217872,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b15366b972ce5e0dd136fad598da39774f7db992","tid":1217872,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:17:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ca188318cad47fd674486e70b697289c9b98aa0","tid":1217872,"uid":80632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"放工好多人轉曬搭巴士啦<br />\n點搞"},{"pid":"417a84a2005ae214dc54eaf60efa91bdc00c4700","tid":1217872,"uid":53374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:18:30.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f0c21e08429a35ad30cb72966d88a4bbbf7c276e","tid":1217872,"uid":162979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:18:34.000Z","msg":"唔幫你推"},{"pid":"9403891f800fb741c242e20ef3e35b50430d72bc","tid":1217872,"uid":259319,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1ca188318cad47fd674486e70b697289c9b98aa0","tid":1217872,"uid":80632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"放工好多人轉曬搭巴士啦<br />\n點搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:20:06.000Z","msg":"目的只係塞返工，少咗人搭港鐵，就會多咗路面嘅車，等路面都塞爆佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b681aa0165fdc338072c4897cecce99e46a71ddb","tid":1217872,"uid":57571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ca188318cad47fd674486e70b697289c9b98aa0","tid":1217872,"uid":80632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"放工好多人轉曬搭巴士啦<br />\n點搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:20:22.000Z","msg":"淨搞返工"},{"pid":"eef578b7d032edf4713599f7b958edb888c2c78a","tid":1217872,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c21e08429a35ad30cb72966d88a4bbbf7c276e","tid":1217872,"uid":162979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:18:34.000Z","msg":"唔幫你推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4291b91cd6bac24b2338f7791884b03a0b34d05","tid":1217872,"uid":259319,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:22:27.0